TONES is a program to test the audio of the Project Burro 2D game engine.

When the TONES 'game' is run, it presents a set of slider bar controls

Initial Pitch
Attack Pitch
Sustain Pitch
Decay Pitch
Attack Duration
Decay Duration
Sustain Duration
Release Duration
Attack Amplitude
Sustain Amplitude
Duty

up/down jumps from slider to slider
left/right adjusts the slider
A plays it as tone
B plays it as noise